                <h1 class="title">About Us</h1>
                <p><strong>@ViewBag.Client.Name</strong> is a South Africa based tour operator selling ready-packaged and tailor-made holidays to South Africa, Zanzibar, Mauritius, Victoria Falls and Thailand. We are part of Web Travel Brands, who are also responsible for running Mango Travel Packages - the packaging division of Mango Airlines in South Africa.</p>
                <p>With over 30 years’ experience in senior management positions in prominent South African airlines, hotel groups, retail travel agents, online tours operators and travel publications, our staff are committed to offering travel services of the highest quality.</p>
                <p>We have access to the best airline, car hire and hotel rates allowing us to ensure that you are always getting the best price possible by booking with us, saving you the trouble of booking directly yourself. Our suppliers that we deal with are carefully selected, reputable and are providers of quality products and services.</p>
                <p>We will tailor-make your holiday to suit your specific needs and budget and ensure that you have a hassle-free experience from beginning to end. Our goal is to offer the ultimate in personal attention and best value-for-money travel deals. For immediate availability and pricing for South Africa and Zanzibar, you can access our online portal - it’s as simple as that! This means that the price you see is the price you pay – one of the advantages of‘real -time, online bookings’. In time, all of our products will be available for immediate online bookings, however for our other packages at the moment you can speak to one of our friendly staff for that personal touch. We are just a quick phone call or email away.</p>
                <p>Experience the joys and inspiration of travel. Our passion is travel!</p>
                <p><strong>“To travel is to live”</strong><span style="font-style: italic; font-size: smaller"> Hans Christian Andersen</span></p>
